{"tid":1217484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(自由黨成員) 吳龍飛︰將拉隊參加周日民陣遊行","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:46:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"00a536eb31a193b9af372369b636dc33bfa2d5e2","tid":1217484,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190613/59711557?fbclid=IwAR3UqtoFPJVVMt4_ujuXmBiaCHLlkCz0VgnQRDPAlt1pXd--NeKymYU9BLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711557%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3UqtoFPJVVMt4_ujuXmBiaCHLlkCz0VgnQRDPAlt1pXd--NeKymYU9BLM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=908228a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711557%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3UqtoFPJVVMt4_ujuXmBiaCHLlkCz0VgnQRDPAlt1pXd--NeKymYU9BLM&h=6f186b07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190613/59711557?fbclid=IwAR3UqtoFPJVVMt4_ujuXmBiaCHLlkCz0VgnQRDPAlt1pXd--NeKymYU9BLM</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年06月13日<br />\n【引渡惡法】自由黨員發起全港業主反送中 吳龍飛︰拉隊周日遊行<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0613 19:13 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0613 16:33<br />\n<br />\n【新增吳龍飛訪問】<br />\n<br />\n自由黨黨員吳龍飛發起「香港業主反對修訂《逃犯條例》聯署」，逼使立法會建制派議員，包括4位自由黨議員轉呔反對送中惡法，他接受電話訪問時表示，網上聯署加實體聯署已有約3,000多位業主參與。<br />\n<br />\n吳龍飛對昨日金鐘發生大型警民衝突感到傷心難過，他表示理解走上街頭抗爭年輕人的感受。作為香港業主，他對政府無視港人反對逃犯條例修訂訴求，感到驚恐及絕望，擔心一國兩制不保，導致樓價大跌，失業率升，嚴重影響正在供樓的業主，令香港喪失國際城市特質。他指已將一眾業主的憂慮向4位自由黨議員反映，但他們並無接納，因此已打算退黨，「我哋好多商人都好怕條例嘅灰色地帶，商界相當憂慮，但又唔敢發聲，香港越少規則越好，否則就會影響外來投資。」<strong>他表示在自由黨內、商界、地產界都有很多人憂慮，他正在組織一眾業主參加星期日（16日）的大遊行，希望政府撤回修訂。他同時警告所有建制派議員，不要與民意為敵，否則「票債票償！」 </strong>"},{"pid":"f2ce91497eec6ac9f0bbe17a1f7c92526b3d378d","tid":1217484,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9776ea62a95adee3a4f801ab98f52af88fe5bc2c","tid":1217484,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eaef3d5fbb19bdfe0d02752f8a3d342c5d39359","tid":1217484,"uid":47112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"正路 自由黨一堆商家"},{"pid":"a276592d5e20b9e75b6ab8cc397e94ead42b3e0e","tid":1217484,"uid":54959,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"自由黨又做關鍵一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024127248eac2da19395986c82a7f1f9abc21525","tid":1217484,"uid":10637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a276592d5e20b9e75b6ab8cc397e94ead42b3e0e","tid":1217484,"uid":54959,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"自由黨又做關鍵一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"想當年23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efab0204f0a22093ab66865b8efc8119ec8ad27","tid":1217484,"uid":91227,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a276592d5e20b9e75b6ab8cc397e94ead42b3e0e","tid":1217484,"uid":54959,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"自由黨又做關鍵一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"做左都唔夠票"},{"pid":"eb55abb9b65be45748ec9936279d3ce5444ff662","tid":1217484,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"反了反了！"},{"pid":"10f5111cfeb27cf59f33ba91a72e607ecdafa1bb","tid":1217484,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"他同時警告所有建制派議員，不要與民意為敵，否則「票債票償！」<br />\n<br />\n今年出年選舉年，林鄭贏咗今次未來幾年就難行"},{"pid":"a1c22f72a59014f988b3c1c4e51e8f19f9666b5f","tid":1217484,"uid":157938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">出席遊行 完結 好好休息 <br />\n出席集會 做好分工<br />\n<br />\n每次都要留力 <br />\n因為呢場係硬仗 <br />\n<br />\n唔每次都出 就會輸 <br />\n<br />\n法國黃背心 以致所有歷史 <br />\n都不會一次成功 <br />\n<br />\n更何況依家正面對柒婆 極權統治 <br />\n<br />\n香港人 撐住！！ </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"feebf14d4504d64fe594860424e86fcef967445e","tid":1217484,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a866e0bb774303263612760e636aca704194f4","tid":1217484,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"自由黨由細嘅扯頭纜倒弋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7bebc2fdc8086ee339eeb0dce5fbe8c98e5942","tid":1217484,"uid":47112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32a866e0bb774303263612760e636aca704194f4","tid":1217484,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"自由黨由細嘅扯頭纜倒弋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"咁先夠自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365571b9c8dcb73a5fdf10445dec31c76c5d4ff","tid":1217484,"uid":148987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"有突破<br />\n不如叫埋張建宗，佢咁多樓"},{"pid":"ce86563b89b9861b6f067cfc878d092bc186028e","tid":1217484,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"咁早出聲似等人搵佢之後再縮沙"},{"pid":"8e8211ae3808cb0962242a82e12ae25b01b5c9ba","tid":1217484,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a276592d5e20b9e75b6ab8cc397e94ead42b3e0e","tid":1217484,"uid":54959,"like"